Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add extra tools and CFEngine modifications for LMDB.

---
 libraries/liblmdb/Makefile |   3 +
 libraries/liblmdb/lmdump.c | 128 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 libraries/liblmdb/lmmgr.c  | 202 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 333 insertions(+)
